title: Talent Vs. Choice, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO181
itunes:title: Talent Vs. Choice, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO181
description: Does loads of talent determine your success? No. So stop looking at other people and say, "Man, if I had his talent, I'd be able to achieve my goals." That's total bullsh*t.  Here's the reality: It's not lack of talent or ability or circumstances that keep you from success. It's the failure to make the right choices. You have to know what to do and to choose to do it.
